translate english start_915cb944:

    # "It's only when I hear the sounds of shuffling feet and supplies being put away that I realize that the lecture's over."
    "直到听见收拾物品的窸窣声和杂乱的脚步声，我才意识到讲座已经结束了。"

# game/script.rpy:20
translate english start_d48fb984:

    # "Professor Eileen's lectures are usually interesting, but today I just couldn't concentrate on it."
    "艾琳教授的课通常都很有趣，但今天我实在无法集中注意力。"

# game/script.rpy:22
translate english start_622654e3:

    # "I've had a lot of other thoughts on my mind...thoughts that culminate in a question."
    "我满脑子都在想着别的事情...这些思绪最终凝结成了一个疑问。"

# game/script.rpy:24
translate english start_5aee3489:

    # "It's a question that I've been meaning to ask a certain someone."
    "这个疑问我一直想向某个人提出。"

# game/script.rpy:29
translate english start_66c6d238:

    # "When we come out of the university, I spot her right away."
    "刚走出大学校门，我一眼就看见了她。"

# game/script.rpy:34
translate english start_1d44d9d7:

    # "I've known Sylvie since we were kids. She's got a big heart and she's always been a good friend to me."
    "我和西尔维从小就认识。她心地善良，一直都是我的好朋友。"

# game/script.rpy:36
translate english start_1c8af99f:

    # "But recently... I've felt that I want something more."
    "但最近...我渴望更进一步的关系。"

# game/script.rpy:38
translate english start_17a1771f:

    # "More than just talking, more than just walking home together when our classes end."
    "不仅仅是聊天，不仅仅是课后一起回家。"

# game/script.rpy:57
translate english rightaway_cf214f74:

    # s "Hi there! How was class?"
    s "嗨！课上得怎么样？"

# game/script.rpy:59
translate english rightaway_f5f51c33:

    # m "Good..."
    m "还不错..."

# game/script.rpy:61
translate english rightaway_027fd9f0:

    # "I can't bring myself to admit that it all went in one ear and out the other."
    "我实在不好意思承认自己左耳进右耳出。"

# game/script.rpy:63
translate english rightaway_1e626e6b:

    # m "Are you going home now? Wanna walk back with me?"
    m "你现在要回家吗？一起走好吗？"

# game/script.rpy:65
translate english rightaway_ed1dfb9d:

    # s "Sure!"
    s "好呀！"

# game/script.rpy:70
translate english rightaway_03faae39:

    # "After a short while, we reach the meadows just outside the neighborhood where we both live."
    "不一会儿，我们就来到了居住社区外的那片草地。"

# game/script.rpy:72
translate english rightaway_b3b54d3c:

    # "It's a scenic view I've grown used to. Autumn is especially beautiful here."
    "这是我早已看惯的风景。这里的秋天格外美丽。"

# game/script.rpy:74
translate english rightaway_8f173bb5:

    # "When we were children, we played in these meadows a lot, so they're full of memories."
    "小时候我们经常在这片草地上玩耍，这里满载着回忆。"

# game/script.rpy:76
translate english rightaway_aa84c954:

    # m "Hey... Umm..."
    m "那个...嗯..."

# game/script.rpy:81
translate english rightaway_79becbf8:

    # "She turns to me and smiles. She looks so welcoming that I feel my nervousness melt away."
    "她转身对我微笑。那亲切的模样让我的紧张感渐渐消散。"

# game/script.rpy:83
translate english rightaway_6a5d032c:

    # "I'll ask her...!"
    "我要向她表白...！"

# game/script.rpy:85
translate english rightaway_29e68260:

    # m "Ummm... Will you..."
    m "嗯...你愿不愿意..."

# game/script.rpy:87
translate english rightaway_6c267868:

    # m "Will you be my artist for a visual novel?"
    m "你愿意做我视觉小说的画师吗？"

# game/script.rpy:91
translate english rightaway_16b8cb94:

    # "Silence."
    "一阵沉默。"

# game/script.rpy:93
translate english rightaway_289664f3:

    # "She looks so shocked that I begin to fear the worst. But then..."
    "她震惊的表情让我心里一沉。但随后..."

# game/script.rpy:99
translate english rightaway_8cb5deeb:

    # s "Sure, but what's a \"visual novel?\"" nointeract
    s "Sure, but what's a \"visual novel?\"" nointeract

# game/script.rpy:110
translate english game_65cca574:

    # m "It's a kind of videogame you can play on your computer or a console."
    m "这是一种可以在电脑或游戏机上玩的电子游戏。"

# game/script.rpy:112
translate english game_da120cd2:

    # m "Visual novels tell a story with pictures and music."
    m "视觉小说会用画面和音乐来讲述故事。"

# game/script.rpy:114
translate english game_0157c4d2:

    # m "Sometimes, you also get to make choices that affect the outcome of the story."
    m "有时候还能通过选项影响故事结局。"

# game/script.rpy:116
translate english game_68b33461:

    # s "So it's like those choose-your-adventure books?"
    s "就像那种选择冒险的书？"

# game/script.rpy:118
translate english game_fa834128:

    # m "Exactly! I've got lots of different ideas that I think would work."
    m "没错！我有很多不同的创意点子。"

# game/script.rpy:120
translate english game_d9b28ade:

    # m "And I thought maybe you could help me...since I know how you like to draw."
    m "我想也许你能帮我...毕竟我知道你喜欢画画。"

# game/script.rpy:122
translate english game_eaa56bc9:

    # m "It'd be hard for me to make a visual novel alone."
    m "我一个人很难完成视觉小说。"

# game/script.rpy:126
translate english game_9befd1bf:

    # s "Well, sure! I can try. I just hope I don't disappoint you."
    s "当然可以！我愿意试试。希望不会让你失望。"

# game/script.rpy:128
translate english game_c788ae90:

    # m "You know you could never disappoint me, Sylvie."
    m "你永远不会让我失望的，西尔维。"

# game/script.rpy:137
translate english book_4221b3bd:

    # m "It's like an interactive book that you can read on a computer or a console."
    m "就像一本可以在电脑或游戏机上阅读的互动书。"

# game/script.rpy:141
translate english book_4cfd8044:

    # s "Interactive?"
    s "互动？"

# game/script.rpy:143
translate english book_b9c732c8:

    # m "You can make choices that lead to different events and endings in the story."
    m "你可以通过选择触发不同的事件和故事结局。"

# game/script.rpy:145
translate english book_1c7ac61a:

    # s "So where does the \"visual\" part come in?"
    s "那'视觉'的部分体现在哪里呢？"

# game/script.rpy:147
translate english book_763f25a8:

    # m "Visual novels have pictures and even music, sound effects, and sometimes voice acting to go along with the text."
    m "视觉小说配有插图、背景音乐、音效，有时还有角色配音。"

# game/script.rpy:151
translate english book_2277f2aa:

    # s "I see! That certainly sounds like fun. I actually used to make webcomics way back when, so I've got lots of story ideas."
    s "明白了！听起来确实很有趣。其实我以前画过网络漫画，有很多故事创意。"

# game/script.rpy:153
translate english book_ccd3e9b0:

    # m "That's great! So...would you be interested in working with me as an artist?"
    m "太棒了！所以...你愿意以画师身份和我合作吗？"

# game/script.rpy:155
translate english book_e325967b:

    # s "I'd love to!"
    s "非常乐意！"

# game/script.rpy:164
translate english marry_4509e340:

    # "And so, we become a visual novel creating duo."
    "就这样，我们组成了视觉小说创作二人组。"

# game/script.rpy:169
translate english marry_0f82ff7f:

    # "Over the years, we make lots of games and have a lot of fun making them."
    "这些年来，我们制作了许多游戏，享受创作的乐趣。"

# game/script.rpy:173
translate english marry_08e24a18:

    # "Our first game is based on one of Sylvie's ideas, but afterwards I get to come up with stories of my own, too."
    "我们的第一部作品改编自西尔维的创意，之后我也开始构思自己的故事。"

# game/script.rpy:175
translate english marry_285256a1:

    # "We take turns coming up with stories and characters and support each other to make some great games!"
    "我们轮流负责故事和角色设计，互相支持创作优秀的游戏！"

# game/script.rpy:177
translate english marry_27260f18:

    # "And one day..."
    "直到有一天..."

# game/script.rpy:182
translate english marry_bf690666:

    # s "Hey..."
    s "喂..."

# game/script.rpy:184
translate english marry_7a5c1899:

    # m "Yes?"
    m "怎么了？"

# game/script.rpy:188
translate english marry_3c154e68:

    # s "Will you marry me?"
    s "你愿意娶我吗？"

# game/script.rpy:190
translate english marry_8bcbc4b9:

    # m "What? Where did this come from?"
    m "什么？怎么突然说这个？"

# game/script.rpy:194
translate english marry_f913278c:

    # s "Come on, how long have we been dating?"
    s "拜托，我们都交往多久了？"

# game/script.rpy:196
translate english marry_4ba892a0:

    # m "A while..."
    m "有一阵子了..."

# game/script.rpy:200
translate english marry_39d7f0df:

    # s "These last few years we've been making visual novels together, spending time together, helping each other..."
    s "这些年来我们一起制作视觉小说，朝夕相处，互相扶持..."

# game/script.rpy:202
translate english marry_1516df50:

    # s "I've gotten to know you and care about you better than anyone else. And I think the same goes for you, right?"
    s "我比任何人都更了解你、在乎你。我想你也一样，对吧？"

# game/script.rpy:204
translate english marry_3234b0ab:

    # m "Sylvie..."
    m "西尔维..."

# game/script.rpy:208
translate english marry_8179b35b:

    # s "But I know you're the indecisive type. If I held back, who knows when you'd propose?"
    s "但我知道你是优柔寡断的类型。如果我不主动，谁知道你什么时候才会求婚？"

# game/script.rpy:212
translate english marry_373937d9:

    # s "So will you marry me?"
    s "所以愿意和我结婚吗？"

# game/script.rpy:214
translate english marry_857958dc:

    # m "Of course I will! I've actually been meaning to propose, honest!"
    m "当然愿意！其实我也一直打算求婚的，真的！"

# game/script.rpy:216
translate english marry_81ed468b:

    # s "I know, I know."
    s "知道啦知道啦。"

# game/script.rpy:218
translate english marry_1c4ae954:

    # m "I guess... I was too worried about timing. I wanted to ask the right question at the right time."
    m "可能...我太在意时机了。总想在最佳时刻提出最完美的问题。"

# game/script.rpy:222
translate english marry_0db38565:

    # s "You worry too much. If only this were a visual novel and I could pick an option to give you more courage!"
    s "你想太多了。要是这是视觉小说就好了，我就能选个选项给你勇气！"

# game/script.rpy:227
translate english marry_ca27786f:

    # "We get married shortly after that."
    "不久后我们结婚了。"

# game/script.rpy:229
translate english marry_621ed4fc:

    # "Our visual novel duo lives on even after we're married...and I try my best to be more decisive."
    "婚后我们依然保持着视觉小说二人组...而我也努力变得更有决断力。"

# game/script.rpy:231
translate english marry_3c7f0bf0:

    # "Together, we live happily ever after even now."
    "从此我们永远幸福地生活在一起。"

# game/script.rpy:233
translate english marry_2ad49007:

    # "{b}Good Ending{/b}."
    "{b}幸福结局{/b}。"

# game/script.rpy:239
translate english later_3c679c17:

    # "I can't get up the nerve to ask right now. With a gulp, I decide to ask her later."
    "我现在鼓不起勇气开口。咽了咽口水，决定改天再问。"

# game/script.rpy:244
translate english later_a77741b6:

    # "But I'm an indecisive person."
    "但我天生优柔寡断。"

# game/script.rpy:246
translate english later_982e14b6:

    # "I couldn't ask her that day and I end up never being able to ask her."
    "那天没能说出口，结果永远失去了告白的机会。"

# game/script.rpy:248
translate english later_f0f9a061:

    # "I guess I'll never know the answer to my question now..."
    "我想现在永远得不到那个问题的答案了..."

# game/script.rpy:250
translate english later_f5219ac2:

    # "{b}Bad Ending{/b}."
    "{b}坏结局{/b}。"

